    "original_title": "Queens: Old Bowery Bay Road - 29th Street",
    "text": "Old Bowery Bay Road, south side, between 29th and 31st Streets, showing a rear view of the John Alsop farmhouse, viewed from 21st Ave. Some of the owners of this house were John Alsop 1852 and C. Debevoise 1860-1873. This house was demolished in March or May of 1925. No. 20-54 31st Street, a four story apartment house now occupies the site. This is a set of three views.\n\nMay 1923.\n\nEugene L. Ambruster Collection.\n",
